name: Emma Thynn
summary: The Marchioness of Bath, Emma Thynn, has declined to offer advice to Meghan Markle despite sharing a connection to royalty. Thynn's decision comes amid the airing of the third week of Celebrity MasterChef 2024, where celebrity contestants prepare culinary dishes. One contestant, Gregg Wallace, expressed his refusal to consume a dish due to its unappealing nature. Despite her exit from the competition, another contestant expressed satisfaction with her performance. name: Mikel Merino
summary: Arsenal have bolstered their midfield with the signing of Mikel Merino from Real Sociedad on a long-term deal. The transfer fee is reported to be worth up to £31.6 million, including add-ons. Merino is a Spain international and has been described as a player of "huge quality." Arsenal manager Unai Emery is reportedly a big admirer of Merino and believes he will be a valuable asset to the team. The signing of Merino is part of Arsenal's ongoing transfer strategy, which has also seen the departure of midfielder Aaron Ramsey to Juventus.

name: Keir Starmer
summary: In a speech on August 27, 2024, UK Labour Party leader Keir Starmer outlined his plans to "fix the foundations" of the country. He warned that the upcoming Autumn Budget would be "painful" and that "things will get worse before they get better." Starmer's speech was seen as a political gamble, as he acknowledged the challenges facing the country and promised to "turn the corner" on Brexit and reset the UK-EU relationship. Despite these warnings, Starmer also blamed the Conservative Party for Labour's own cronyism scandal, highlighting the deep divisions within British politics.

name: Barcelona
summary: Barcelona secured a narrow 2-1 victory over Athletic Club in their La Liga encounter. Meanwhile, the club's financial struggles continue to make headlines, with doubts cast over the benefits of hosting the America's Cup in Barcelona due to concerns about tourism. Despite these challenges, Barcelona recently loaned Vitor Roque to Real Betis Balompié and managed to register new signing Olmo for their upcoming match against Rayo Vallecano. However, the club's chaotic management and financial instability have raised concerns about its future. Amidst rumors of Hansi Flick potentially becoming the new manager, betting previews and rankings of Barcelona's top goalscorers are also circulating. Additionally, local residents in Barcelona express opposition to the America's Cup, citing elitism and lack of transparency surrounding related tourism plans.
